detaileddescription.para: A benchmark that evaluates the performance of the cardinality check in MERGE operations.

To run this benchmark for spark-3.3: ./gradlew -DsparkVersions=3.3 :iceberg-spark:iceberg-spark-extensions-3.3_2.12:jmh -PjmhIncludeRegex=MergeCardinalityCheckBenchmark -PjmhOutputPath=benchmark/iceberg-merge-cardinality-check-benchmark.txt
